              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Liquid scintillators, NE 213. 2 horizontal cylinder",
                " (3.81 cm diam. * 3.81 cm) mounted on XP1020 and 56AVP",
                "phototubes. Shielded from direct neutron by a common",
                "steel wedge. Neutron-gamma discrimination applied. (For",
                " scattered neutrons)",
                "50 micron thick naton 136 scintillator foil mounted on",
                "an XP1021 phototube. (Associated alpha detection)."
              ]
            }
